{"id":862412946,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"9Â months","timestamp":1671501426,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/862412946/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Roman to Integer","memory":"6 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int romanToInt(string s) {\n        int res=0;\n        char roman[7]={'I','V','X','L','C','D','M'};\n        int id[s.length()];\n        int value[7]={1,5,10,50,100,500,1000};\n        for (int i=0;i<s.length();i++)\n        {\n            for(int j=0;j<7;j++)\n            {\n                if (s[i]==roman[j])\n                {\n                    id[i]=j;\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        for(int i=0;i<s.length()-1;i++)\n        {\n            if(id[i]<id[i+1])\n            {\n                res-=value[id[i]];\n            }\n            else\n            {\n                res+=value[id[i]];\n            }\n        }\n        res+=value[id[s.length()-1]];\n        return res;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"roman-to-integer","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
